Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.80,0:00:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了要拯救世界的所有一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.53,0:00:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱离走向毁灭的大崩落危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.44,0:00:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不断旅行的里德，法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.44,0:00:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.11,0:00:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在旅途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停留的海上都市·贝鲁卡纽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.75,0:00:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满了许多的迷团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.25,0:00:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在地下的那些蒙面人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.45,0:00:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目的到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.85,0:00:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有等待里德他们的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.02,0:00:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又将会如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.92,0:00:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样…故事已渐入佳境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.63,0:02:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第8话  晶灵光涡之夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.11,0:02:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.92,0:02:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德  基尔  你们来一下好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  这么晚了还来找我们？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.05,0:02:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂她怪怪的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说梅露蒂她吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.70,0:02:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉拉在发光？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.13,0:02:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好漂亮哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.82,0:03:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好美哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听着！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在要去完成任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.04,0:03:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用法规去制裁我们的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前正是反击的好机会！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.77,0:03:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会闯进敌人茵费利亚的阵地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们趁这时候争取逃走的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.11,0:03:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是无法活着归来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是我们伟大的神·奈雷特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所赐予给我们的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定要活下去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.49,0:03:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活着替我们报仇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.09,0:03:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油   加油…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.00,0:03:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈雷特…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.63,0:03:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期盼吾神奈雷特荣耀满身！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.71,0:04:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.62,0:04:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得像是做了一场漫长的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.66,0:04:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的祈祷即将实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡许久的强大力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.26,0:04:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到觉醒的时刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.43,0:04:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  从祖先继承而来的制裁锁链
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.74,0:04:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来只差大晶灵而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.59,0:04:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这需要大晶灵所拥有的无限力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.86,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会准备应战来阻止那些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.87,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…终于要把那些家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然主要是掌控大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.27,0:05:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在那之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先除掉碍事的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.94,0:05:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得碍事的家伙是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这座岛和赛雷斯提亚有关？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.42,0:05:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.43,0:05:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得上次我们打倒的怪兽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.03,0:05:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的头上的确有艾拉拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.63,0:05:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…地下也有晶灵遗迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.04,0:05:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上梅露蒂昨晚那个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我后来有拐弯抹角的问过她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂是说她昨晚在做梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.21,0:05:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做梦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.14,0:05:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，她说梦到赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.02,0:05:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有听说对赛雷斯提亚人来讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.42,0:05:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉拉是某种传达性质的器官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.36,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果附近有同伴存在的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎会产生激烈的反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.06,0:05:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.13,0:05:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这岛上也有赛雷斯提亚人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.73,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那未免太奇怪了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茵费利亚和赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都没有互相往来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.74,0:06:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连梅露蒂也是很不容易才来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.61,0:06:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.54,0:06:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，里德  你也别光发呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.28,0:06:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也发表一下意见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.58,0:06:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.15,0:06:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛雷斯提亚人到我们这边来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可以讲的这么悠哉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.55,0:06:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛雷斯提亚人是灾祸的根源啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是过去的老旧传说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.59,0:06:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂虽然是赛雷斯提亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她有给我们带来什么灾祸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是世界将毁灭这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已经是够大的灾祸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且我们会开始出来旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追根究底来说也是因为梅露蒂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.11,0:06:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.21,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂…是大家的灾祸根源吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧，你们大家说是不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.79,0:06:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.41,0:07:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂  什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德，你干嘛突然这样做啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.20,0:07:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次换我报仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.67,0:07:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我泼回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.84,0:07:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.25,0:07:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要也抱我下水呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.38,0:07:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德  里德大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.42,0:08:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.93,0:08:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德那个人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是会看出那种状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.70,0:08:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏他那么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.17,0:08:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没害梅露蒂哭出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.54,0:08:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德这个人虽然常常对天空发呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在紧要的关头却非常可靠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.71,0:08:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不过其实也不一定啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.95,0:08:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候…我还真羡慕那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.75,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑又笨  思考也不周密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.48,0:08:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗枝大叶又粗鲁，可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.25,0:08:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却有办法坦率去接纳别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次看到那样的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.76,0:08:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔就觉得顽固的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是有够渺小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.83,0:08:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些话千万不要跟他说哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.37,0:08:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  给我来真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.39,0:09:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔天，领主艾克丝西亚宣布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁卡纽全境的休息日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了庆祝前阵子台风的重建工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.90,0:09:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且让自古以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流传的祭祀再度重现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那项祭典就订名为“海上祭典”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.10,0:09:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是过去这贝鲁卡纽所举行的祭典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂最喜欢祭典了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个海上祭典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得是什么样的祭典？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.81,0:09:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…海上祭典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.31,0:09:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是向海神祈祷的祭典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.72,0:09:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始的日子是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.65,0:09:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就定在大海发亮的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海发亮的夜晚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一年一度产生的不可思议现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.46,0:09:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了半夜大海会闪闪发亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且吹起发亮的风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.43,0:09:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的话刚好是在后天呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真了解耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.63,0:09:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.77,0:09:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今年的海上祭典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以来流传的风俗习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也将再度重视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.67,0:10:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…这个风俗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在这一天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许女性对男性…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作出爱的告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性向男性…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…做出爱的告白？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.88,0:10:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.99,0:10:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.82,0:10:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚决要在海上祭典那晚执行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.93,0:10:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天宅邸的戒备应该比较松懈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.47,0:10:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就…  不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.14,0:10:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能轻易决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西非人类的智慧所能及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.48,0:10:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.74,0:10:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再静观其变吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.15,0:10:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那些家伙来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对有做什么安排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.52,0:10:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等那个时候再…  为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.82,0:10:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为需要用到那个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.49,0:10:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.69,0:10:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，她是塔斯帖克的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.68,0:11:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.01,0:11:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些书要放哪里啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，基鲁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.82,0:11:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.26,0:11:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想问你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了要调查贝鲁卡纽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.49,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和赛雷斯提亚的有的没有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.40,0:11:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我来帮忙的人可是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你竟然在给我发呆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再啰嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.14,0:11:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把下一堆资料搬过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.17,0:11:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么口气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.64,0:11:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，法拉  你也替我说说他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.95,0:11:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.62,0:11:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…糟糕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.06,0:11:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也真是的，到底在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家到底是哪根筋不对劲了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.80,0:12:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.17,0:12:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.64,0:12:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做了祭典那晚要穿的服装哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得好不好看？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮，你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.21,0:12:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是午觉睡太多睡迷糊了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.08,0:12:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.65,0:12:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望在明天海上祭典的晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能快点向里德大人告白呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.42,0:12:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.63,0:12:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.76,0:12:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们两个…要告白？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，因为里德大人对我来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个温柔又可靠的大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.97,0:12:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂也要谢谢他那天陪我玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.14,0:12:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕你们…这么坦率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有话…要跟我说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.42,0:13:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的海上祭典开始之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请你独自到东边的海湾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话可以现在说没关系啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有点不方便…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.00,0:13:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要明天说才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了，那我明天就等你说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.84,0:13:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你一定要到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.08,0:13:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有话…要跟我说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.25,0:13:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请你答应我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.82,0:13:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.08,0:13:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的海上祭典开始之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.69,0:13:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请你独自到东边的海湾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东边的海湾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.19,0:13:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  那明天见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.70,0:13:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.23,0:13:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么说定了  好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.07,0:13:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后到了海上祭典当天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  请注意看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要参加祭典的服装哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.73,0:14:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋  都没反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不然穿去给里德大人看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.64,0:14:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是里德不在耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.11,0:14:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔，你知不知道里德去哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找里德的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.25,0:14:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说到附近的无人岛游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.75,0:14:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概又是对着天空发呆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还说傍晚就会回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.99,0:14:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.92,0:15:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个位子有人坐吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.80,0:15:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看连问都不必问了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.03,0:15:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很鸡婆耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典差不多快开始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.64,0:15:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.95,0:15:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂和可莉娜…向里德告白？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.35,0:15:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是告白其实是挺可爱的告白啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.29,0:15:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是被打败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们实在是有够坦白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.95,0:15:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过或许是我太拘束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.29,0:15:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的好像你有心上人似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.86,0:15:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你自己呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.47,0:16:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…连我自己也不确定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.77,0:16:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的心意到底是怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.91,0:16:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果是半斤八两啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.74,0:16:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.68,0:16:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在自言自语啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.72,0:16:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了  去参加祭典吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.53,0:16:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.93,0:16:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…梅露蒂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.17,0:16:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有…我有话要跟你说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.70,0:16:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思就是人不可貌相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且偏偏还是那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.24,0:16:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主动去邀里德呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.51,0:16:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的那个我也有看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.08,0:16:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是约在东边的海湾见面对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.95,0:16:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.85,0:16:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你也看到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.89,0:17:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真叫人意外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.69,0:17:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的年龄明明差很多的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.13,0:17:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗我倒觉得蛮接近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.60,0:17:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得里德他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好很适合姐弟恋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.04,0:17:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在说谁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.68,0:17:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚祭典开始了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既没找到里德大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂也没来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.59,0:17:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.52,0:18:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样不是脚踏两条船吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.86,0:18:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.03,0:18:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走？去东边的海湾吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.33,0:18:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德要喜欢谁我是管不着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.50,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反倒是担心普拉提亚和蜜妮玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.67,0:18:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.94,0:18:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果因为里德\N而害她们吵架的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.74,0:18:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.78,0:18:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，同样是女人的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.84,0:18:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能坐视不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有同感  我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.41,0:18:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.78,0:18:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个都说有话要跟我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.39,0:18:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了省去麻烦  干脆就一起听吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.06,0:18:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德他还真率直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.77,0:18:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是太率直的话  也是一种罪过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快一点的话里德就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…普拉提亚她们就会出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.38,0:18:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再多看一眼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.01,0:19:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要先走了哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.38,0:19:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再看一眼就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为自己太不坦率的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.69,0:19:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.16,0:19:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.99,0:19:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的大海发亮的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.36,0:19:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是存在于自然界的小晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.40,0:19:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所产生的晶灵光涡现象啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好令人怀念哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.27,0:19:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂在赛雷斯提亚的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.84,0:19:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾看过同样的景象呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.08,0:19:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂…那天的事我很抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.38,0:19:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.32,0:19:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我也希望能尽快跟你道歉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.32,0:19:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要让自己变得坦率一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是一件相当困难的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.29,0:19:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.93,0:19:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
